Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.18,MainDialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Niche!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:25.91,MainDialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyčisti si zuby!
